Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
getPinDensityMapMode(25.10)                        getPinDensityMapMode(25.10)

Name
       getPinDensityMapMode

Syntax
       getPinDensityMapMode

       [-gridInMicron]

       [-gridInRow]

       [-threshold]

       [-quiet]

       Returns  the  information  about setPinDensityMapMode parameters in the
       Innovus log file and in the Innovus console. Returns the following  in-
       formation:

              * Parameter name

              * Current value

              * Type (Boolean, string, and so on)

              * Source of current value (default, user)

       If you do not specify a parameter, the software displays values for all
       of the setPinDensityMapMode mode parameters.

Related Information
              * reportPinDensityMap

              * setPinDensityMapMode

